### 2) Structured Data Suggestions
- **Ensure Full Coverage**: Include additional types such as `Product` for specific garden shed offerings.
- **Add Ratings**: If applicable, include an `aggregateRating` to provide social proof of product quality.
- **Local Business Schema**: If the organization services a specific area, use `LocalBusiness` schema to enhance local visibility.
- **Breadcrumb List**: Include breadcrumb schema for better site navigation visibility.

Example of Product Schema:

```json
{
  "@type": "Product",
  "name": "Premium Clay Garden Shed",
  "image": "https://www.gardenshedclay.com/images/premium-shed.jpg",
  "description": "Our Premium Clay Garden Shed combines traditional craftsmanship with modern design, perfect for storing tools or creating a cozy outdoor space.",
  "brand": {
    "@type": "Brand",
    "name": "Garden Shed Clay"
  },
  "sku": "GSC-001",
  "offers": {
