    "price": "349.99",
    "itemCondition": "https://schema.org/NewCondition",
    "availability": "https://schema.org/InStock"
  }
}
```

### 3) Keyword Improvements
- **Primary Keywords**: Focus on primary keywords such as "handcrafted garden sheds", "clay garden products", and "sustainable outdoor solutions".
- **Long-Tail Keywords**: Incorporate long-tail keywords like "best garden shed for storage", "custom clay garden sheds", and "eco-friendly garden shed options".
- **Geo-Keywords**: Use geographic modifiers for local SEO, e.g., “Clay City garden shed” or “California garden storage solutions”.
- **Action Words**: Utilize verbs in headings and meta-descriptions, such as “Discover”, “Explore”, or “Enhance your garden with”.

### Conclusion
By implementing these optimized JSON-LD structures, structured data suggestions, and targeted keywords, the content will be well-positioned to rank higher in search results and improve overall visibility in 2026 SEO landscape.